'''热释光测年法'''，或稱'''熱螢光定年法'''，是利用[[热释光效应|热释光效应]]（{{lang|en|thermoluminescence}}）测量含有結晶體的礦物或燒製[[文物|文物]]，自加熱或烧制後經過时间的一种方法。利用热释光效应，可以根据样本所释放[[光子|光子]]的能量判断出样本自从上一次被加热后至今所接受的環境背景[[辐射|辐射]]能量之和，因而估算自加熱時間點至今經過的时间。<ref>[http://china001.com/show_hdr.php?xname=PPDDMV0&dname=400CC51&xpos=7 热释光断代]</ref><ref>[http://smah.uow.edu.au/sees/facilities/UOW002896.html Thermoluminescence (TL) dating] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402114336/http://smah.uow.edu.au/sees/facilities/UOW002896.html |date=2015-04-02 }}, University of Wollongong, Australia; [http://daybreaknuclear.us/bortolot_faq.html Daybreak Corporation, FAQs] {{Wayback|url=http://daybreaknuclear.us/bortolot_faq.html |date=20191029202458 }}; [http://www.arch.ox.ac.uk/luminescence.html Oxford University] {{Wayback|url=http://www.arch.ox.ac.uk/luminescence.html |date=20150402170839 }}; [http://www.oxfordauthentication.com/ Oxford Authentification] {{Wayback|url=http://www.oxfordauthentication.com/ |date=20170720044857 }}, see different prices depending on type</ref><ref>[http://daybreaknuclear.us/tlpaper.pdf "Thermoluminescence dating of art objects"] {{Wayback|url=http://daybreaknuclear.us/tlpaper.pdf |date=20201108110932 }}, V.J. Bortolot, Daybreak Corporation; [http://www.coupdefoudre.com/CurrentArticle/Thermo.html "The Limits of TL", Michel Brent, ''Archaeology Magazine'', Volume 54, Number 1, January/February 2001] {{Wayback|url=http://www.coupdefoudre.com/CurrentArticle/Thermo.html |date=20160304070130 }}</ref>

